	<div id="main">
                
                <h2 style="text-align:center;color:aqua">Who are we?</h2>

                 <ul style="list-style-type:none;text-align:left;color:grey">
                 <li><h3 style="text-align:left;color:grey"> <i>We are a group of passionate liverpool fans who are also associated with the
                 Liverpool World twitter and facebook account. Follow us on our twitter account <a href="https://twitter.com/Liverpool_World" target="_blank" 
                	style="color:grey">@Liverpool_World</a> and like us on facebook. 
                	
                 </i></h3></li>
                 <p>Online since: October, 2014.
                 </ul>
                 
 
                 

                 <h2 style="text-align:center;color:aqua">What do we do?</h2>

                 <ul style="list-style-type:none;text-align:left;color:grey">
                 <li><h3 style="text-align:left;color:grey"> <i>It is a liverpool fan based website aimed for Liverpool 
fans all over the world. We provide match reports, live match telecast,
match highlights, transfer updates, fan articles and live forum discussion on LFC related topics.</i></h3></li>
                 </ul>
                 
                

                 <h2 style="text-align:center;color:aqua">Our aim</h2>

                 <ul style="list-style-type:none;text-align:left;color:grey">
                 <li><h3 style="text-align:left;color:grey"> <i>Our aim is to build the world's largest football fan base 
website and promote young writers who has the ambition of writing
LFC related articles.</i></h3></li>
                 </ul>

                 <h2 style="text-align:center;color:aqua">Join our team</h2>

                 <ul style="list-style-type:none;text-align:left;color:grey">
                 <li><h3 style="text-align:left;color:grey"> <i>We are currently looking for ambitious
Kopites who loves writing about LFC. If you feel like you can do a great job writing articles,
leave us a message at liverpoolworld7@gmail.com, and we will get
back to you.</i></h3></li>
                 </ul>
                 
 
                 
                 
